# Build and Run StegaNet

Use the provided Makefile for multi-file builds:


# For single-file Raylib front-end (if needed)
# Ensure uncommenting int main() in bigl
```
gcc bigl.c -o stegaNet -I/opt/homebrew/include -L/opt/homebrew/lib -lraylib -lm
./stegaNet
```

# For Socket Programming
```
gcc socket_chat.c bigl.c -o StegaNet -I/opt/homebrew/include -L/opt/homebrew/lib -lraylib -lpthread -lm 
-framework OpenGL -framework Cocoa -framework IOKit -framework CoreVideo -framework CoreAudio && ./StegaNet
```